data.description: First time home buyer or investment opportunity. Rented for previous 10 years. This 2 Bedroom 2 Bath offers living room and dining room w new laminate floors; Kitchen w tile floors, granite tops, stainless steel range and microwave, built in spice cabinet; family bath w tile, new carpet in bedrooms. Upstairs not included in square due to ceiling height but there is a bonus room and full bath. Deck. Detached 1 car garage/storage building. Minutes from highway and local colleges.
